net.i2p.crypto

Class HMAC256Generator.HMACKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.i2p.crypto.HMAC256Generator.HMACKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Key, SecretKey, Destroyable
    Enclosing class:
    HMAC256Generator

    static final class HMAC256Generator.HMACKey
extends Object
implements SecretKey
    Like SecretKeySpec but doesn't copy the key in the construtor, for speed. It still returns a copy in getEncoded(), because Mac relies on that, doesn't work otherwise. First 32 bytes are returned in getEncoded(), data may be longer.
    Since:
    0.9.38
